rows.label: qst103605_msg0001
rows.name:
Help me!
These people are threatening me!
They're taking me against my will!

rows.label: qst103605_msg0002
rows.name: Didn't look that way to me...

rows.label: qst103605_msg0003
rows.name:
Why don't we get the story straight
back at Hadashal Palace?

rows.label: qst103605_msg0004
rows.name:
It's true I tell you!
Please believe me!

rows.label: qst103605_msg0006
rows.name:
I've just received word that remnants
of the Brionac rebel forces are heading
for the capital!

rows.label: qst103605_msg0008
rows.name: We need to head there now!

rows.label: qst103605_msg0010
rows.name:
I'll keep an eye on the senator,
don't you worry!

rows.label: qst103605_msg0011
rows.name:
Everyone! Head to Midorl Bridge as
fast as you can!
